                  </hi>. I am a clerk in the house of Gosling and Co., bankars.</p>
               <xptr type="pageFacsimile" doc="185610270087"></xptr>
               <p>On 21st Jane, 202<hi rend="italic">l</hi>. 13<hi rend="italic">s</hi>. 4<hi rend="italic">d</hi>. was paid in to the credit of Mr. Alfred Turner's account—one of the items of that account wag a 50<hi rend="italic">l</hi>. Bank of Eogland note, No. 95320, dated 8th Nov.—there were some drafts, and 54<hi rend="italic">l</hi>. in gold.</p>
               <p>
                  <hi rend="smallCaps">
                     <persName id="t18561027-name-356" type="witnessName">
