                        <interp inst="t18561027-name-356" type="given" value="HENRY HOLMAN"></interp>HENRY HOLMAN SMITH</persName>
                  </hi>. I am a clerk in the issue department of the Bank of England. This 50<hi rend="italic">l</hi>. note, No. 95320, was issued on 21st June; gold was given for it—the name of "Harding, No. 48, High-street, Bow," was given by the person to whom it was issued.</p>
               <p>
                  <hi rend="smallCaps">
                     <persName id="t18561027-name-357" type="witnessName">
